{"word":"Trumpet","slug":"trumpet","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Trumpet</b> Made of ram's horn<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=6&verse=6'>Jos 6:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=6&verse=8'>Jos 6:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=6&verse=13'>Jos 6:13</a><br/> Made of silver<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=10&verse=2'>Num 10:2</a><br/> Uses of, prescribed by Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=10&verse=10'>Num 10:10</a><br/> Used in war<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=39&verse=25'>Job 39:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=4&verse=19'>Jer 4:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=6&verse=1'>Jer 6:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=6&verse=17'>Jer 6:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=42&verse=14'>Jer 42:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=51&verse=27'>Jer 51:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=7&verse=14'>Eze 7:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=2&verse=2'>Amo 2:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=3&verse=6'>Amo 3:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=36&chapter=1&verse=16'>Zep 1:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=14&verse=8'>1Co 14:8</a><br/> Used to summon soldiers:<br/> - By Phinehas<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=6'>Num 31:6</a> <br/> - By Ehud<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=3&verse=27'>Jdg 3:27</a> <br/> - By Gideon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=34'>Jdg 6:34</a> <br/> - By Saul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=13&verse=3'>1Sa 13:3</a> <br/> - By Joab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=2&verse=28'>2Sa 2:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=16'>2Sa 18:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=20&verse=22'>2Sa 20:22</a> <br/> - By Absalom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=10'>2Sa 15:10</a> <br/> - By Sheba<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=20&verse=1'>2Sa 20:1</a> <br/> - By Nehemiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=4&verse=18'>Neh 4:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=4&verse=20'>Neh 4:20</a> <br/> Used by Gideon's soldiers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=7&verse=22'>Jdg 7:22</a><br/> Used in war, of Abijah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=13&verse=12'>2Ch 13:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=13&verse=14'>2Ch 13:14</a><br/> Used in the siege of Jericho<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=6&verse=20'>Jos 6:20</a><br/> Sounded in time of danger<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=33&verse=6'>Eze 33:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=2&verse=1'>Joe 2:1</a><br/> Used at Sinai<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=19'>Exo 19:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=20&verse=18'>Exo 20:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=12&verse=19'>Heb 12:19</a><br/> Used on the great day of atonement<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=27&verse=13'>Isa 27:13</a><br/> Used at the jubilee<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=25&verse=9'>Lev 25:9</a><br/> Used at the bringing up of the ark<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=6&verse=5'>2Sa 6:5</a>; <a href='https://www.word